snippet.title: Stellar Blade x Goddess of Victory - Nikke DLC Trailer | PS5 and PC Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/stellar-blade/

Discover the new Stellar Blade DLC - GODDESS OF VICTORY: NIKKE and get ready for the upcoming PC release of Stellar Blade.

Coming June 2025 only on PS5® console and PC. Purchase and game progression required to unlock.
